<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        
        .logo {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .logo-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            stroke: white;
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 2;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 50px 40px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .token-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .token-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            right: -2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2, #667eea);
            border-radius: 15px;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: gradient-rotate 3s linear infinite;
            background-size: 200% 200%;
        }
        
        @keyframes gradient-rotate {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
        
        .token-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .token-code {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .expiry-info {
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .expiry-icon {
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .expiry-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #856404;
            flex: 1;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .expiry-time {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        
        .footer {
            padding: 30px 40px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #999999;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .app-signature {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #667eea, transparent);
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }
            
            .token-code {
                font-size: 32px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h1>{{appName}}</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello {{name}}! üëã</div>
            
            <p class="message">
                Thank you for signing up with <strong>{{appName}}</strong>! We're excited to have you on board.
                To complete your registration and verify your email address, please use the verification code below.
            </p>
            
            <div class="token-container">
                <div class="token-label">Your Verification Code</div>
                <div class="token-code">{{token}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" style="
                    display: inline-block;
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
                    color: white;
                    padding: 15px 30px;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    border-radius: 50px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
                    transition: all 0.3s ease;
                " onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6)';" 
                   onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4)';">
                    üöÄ Verify Email Now
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #999; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                Or copy and paste this link in your browser: <br>
                <span style="word-break: break-all; color: #667eea;">{{verificationUrl}}</span>
            </p>
            
            <div class="expiry-info">
                <div class="expiry-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
                <div class="expiry-text">
                    This code will expire in <span class="expiry-time">{{expiresIn}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p class="message">
                If you didn't request this verification code, please ignore this email or contact our support team if you have concerns.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email. 
                If you need assistance, please visit our support page.
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text">
                ¬© 2024 <span class="app-signature">{{appName}}</span>. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>